'''卑利得'''<span style="font-size:smaller;">，[[御用大律師|QC]]</span>（{{lang-en|David Perry}}），[[英國|英國]]資深[[刑事|刑事]][[大律師|大律師]]。2021年1月《[[泰晤士報|泰晤士報]]》以大字標題指出，他是起訴[[香港民主運動|香港民主運動]]人士的「恥辱之源」<ref name="jashame">{{cite news |last1=Ames |first1=Jonathan |title=David Perry, QC, a ‘source of shame’ for prosecuting Hong Kong democracy campaigners |url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/david-perry-qc-a-source-of-shame-for-prosecuting-hong-kong-democracy-campaigners-srks5kn3f |publisher=Times Newspapers Limited |date=14 January 2021 |accessdate=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2021-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206024342/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/david-perry-qc-a-source-of-shame-for-prosecuting-hong-kong-democracy-campaigners-srks5kn3f |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
卑利得於[[萊斯特大學|萊斯特大學]]法學學士畢業<ref>{{cite book |title=The Bar List of the United Kingdom |date=1982}}</ref>，在1980年被[[林肯律師學院|林肯律師學院]]授予{{tsl|en|Call to the bar|出庭資格}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Mr David Perry QC |url=https://www.barstandardsboard.org.uk/barristers-register/929FCEF978578B4EA160C42C9F453956.html |website={{tsl|en|Bar Standards Board}} |access-date=17 January 2021 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124153610/https://www.barstandardsboard.org.uk/barristers-register/929FCEF978578B4EA160C42C9F453956.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2006年被冊封為[[御用大律師|御用大律師]] <ref name= Times>{{cite news|last=Gibb|first=Frances|title=Profile: silk who advised on honours charges|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/profile-silk-who-advised-on-honours-charges-jfs0b3kq3rp|work=The Times|date=20 July 2007|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114141654/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/profile-silk-who-advised-on-honours-charges-jfs0b3kq3rp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

卑利得因在[[香港|香港]]數宗備受矚目的政治案件中扮演重要角色而聞名。他曾代表[[香港律政司|香港律政司]]起訴前行政長官[[曾蔭權|曾蔭權]]公職人員行為失當罪<ref name= CNBC>{{cite news|last1=Hollingsworth|first1=Julia|last2=Lau|first2=Chris|title=Donald Tsang jailed 20 months for misconduct, becoming city’s highest-ranked official to be put behind bars|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/21/donald-tsang-jailed-20-months-for-misconduct-becoming-citys-highest-ranked-official-to-be-put-behind-bars.html|work=CNBC|date=21 February 2017|accessdate=2021-01-18|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127202050/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/02/21/donald-tsang-jailed-20-months-for-misconduct-becoming-citys-highest-ranked-official-to-be-put-behind-bars.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 起訴香港民主運動人士 ===
2021年1月，他被香港律政司聘用，起訴[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]的創辦人[[黎智英|黎智英]]，以及其他八名在2019年8月於街頭抗議[[中共|中共]]政權鎮壓[[反送中運動|反送中運動]]的民主運動人士<ref name="jashame"/><ref name=scmp1>{{cite web|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3117441/hong-kong-justice-department-hires-queens-counsel|title=Hong Kong justice department hires Queen’s Counsel David Perry to prosecute protest case against Jimmy Lai, eight others|first=Chris|last=Lau|work=[[South_China_Morning_Post|South China Morning Post]]|date=12 January 2021|access-date=12 January 2021|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128110756/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3117441/hong-kong-justice-department-hires-queens-counsel|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括[[李柱銘|李柱銘]]、[[李卓人|李卓人]]、[[梁國雄|梁國雄]]、[[何俊仁|何俊仁]]等。

卑利得的決定受到了[[英國下議院|英國下議院]]外交事務委員會主席[[托馬斯·圖根達特|董勤達]]及[[工黨_(英國)|工黨]][[英國上議院|上議院]]議員{{tsl|en|Lord Adonis|阿多尼斯勳爵}}的質疑。

1月14日，英國前外相[[聶偉敬|聶偉敬]]爵士批評卑利得的決定，並指出很明顯審判是由於中國政府決心摧毀香港的民主運動而進行。聶偉敬提醒大眾，[[英國最高法院|英國最高法院]]前院長[[何熙怡|何熙怡]]女男爵承認，如果她同意在香港審理案件，她將有一個「嚴重的道德問題而問自己」<ref name="mrrule">{{cite news |last1=Rifkind |first1=Malcolm |title=Hong Kong's rule of law is being extinguished |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/01/14/hong-kongs-rule-law-extinguished/ |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |date=14 January 2021 |accessdate=2021-01-18 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129225112/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2021/01/14/hong-kongs-rule-law-extinguished/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1月17日，英國外相[[藍韜文|藍韜文]]受訪時批評卑利得唯利是圖，指其良心如何過意得去，認為他應該根據大律師行為守則拒絕受聘<ref name= Times2>{{cite news|last=Wintour|first1=Patrick|title=Raab takes aim at ‘mercenary’ barrister over Hong Kong case|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/news/raab-takes-aim-at-mercenary-barrister-over-hong-kong-case-d6q5q0wrf?fbclid=IwAR15GdCiqEsGdKJCLOagEKpR4TTBRaWFoYJeWfQUCtHzsjezAp1FgTnZP2g|publisher=Times Newspapers Limited|date=18 January 2021}}</ref>。

